org.jhove2.app.util.traverser
Class ReportableInstanceTraverser

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.app.util.traverser.ReportableInstanceTraverser

public class ReportableInstanceTraverser
extends Object

Traverses instance of a reportable object, collecting reportable feature information, including dotted path to reportable members Intended for use in generating "dotted names" for Assessment configuration NOTE: can only detect inner reportable classes to one level of nesting

Author:
smorrissey
